videos.headline: Ole Miss Ta'amu connects with Lodge for TD
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu finds a wide open DaMarkus Lodge for the 37-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ole Miss Ta'amu finds Brown for  31-yard TD
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu throws short to A.J. Brown who dives in for a 31-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ole Miss Wilkins finds space for a 51 -yard gain
videos.description: Jordan Wilkins bursts up field for a big gain of 51-yards.

videos.headline: Ole Miss Ta'amu runs in untouched  for 8-yard TD
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu calls his own number for a 8-yard touchdown extending the Rebels' lead.

videos.headline: Ole Miss Ta'amu lobs it up to Brown for 27-yard TD
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu gets his fourth touchdown of the first half on a 27-yard pass to  A.J. Brown.

videos.headline: Louisiana Lafayette's Calais gets loose for a 31-yard TD
videos.description: Raymond Calais finds a crease and finishes off the 31-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Ole Miss Ta'amu scores 5th TD of the game
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu tucks it and runs in for the 1-yard touchdown. Ta'amu has two rushing touchdowns and three passing touchdowns in the game.

videos.headline: Luke discusses Ta'amu, success of offense
videos.description: Ole Miss head coach Matt Luke likes his team's offensive tempo and wants to see more energy in the second half.

videos.headline: Louisiana Lafayette's Malone takes reverse for 52 yards
videos.description: Ryheem Malone takes the double reverse for a 52-yard gain.

videos.headline: Ole Miss Lodge leaps over defender for 48-yard grab
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu lobs it up to DaMarkus Lodge who comes down with it for a 48-yard gain.

videos.headline: Ole Miss Wilkins runs in untouched for TD
videos.description: Jordan Wilkins goes up the middle for the 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisiana Lafayette's Davis calls his own number for the 10-yard TD
videos.description: Jordan Davis keeps it on fourth down and runs in for a 10-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Lousiana Lafayette's Davis runs untouched for 31-yard TD
videos.description: Jordan Davis runs up the middle on the QB draw for a 31-yard touchdown.
